        {
            "title": "日股半日跌逾1%　失守53000點關口",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股向下，日經指數失守53000點關口，創1星期新低。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">指數半日報52931點，跌652點，跌幅1.22%。</p>\n</div>",
