        {
            "title": "中港股市跌幅齊擴大 恒指一度再跌200點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人民幣強勢，中港股市卻雙雙向下，早市中段跌勢均加劇。恒生指數稍早前曾跌至26363點，跌200點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至上午約10時29分，恒指報26376點，跌187點或0.71%；恒生科技指數挫1.46%。多隻重磅科股受壓，騰訊(00700)跌約2%，阿里巴巴(09988)也跌約1%，中芯(00981)更挫約3.6%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">相反，滙控(00005)反彈約1.3%，泡泡瑪特(09992)昨斥約2.51億元回購，今早股價應聲一度升逾10%，現時升幅收窄至約8.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深兩市股指今早初段均高開低走，上證綜指失守4100點，暫跌逾0.5%，深證成指更跌約1.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15595999-%e4%b8%ad%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e9%bd%8a%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e4%b8%80%e5%ba%a6%e5%86%8d%e8%b7%8c200%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 10:35:17",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "泡泡瑪特昨斥2.51億元回購 股價今早最多飆逾10%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泡泡瑪特(09992)股份經過近期相對弱勢後，公司終於「出手」回購，於昨天動用2.51億元回購140萬股。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股今早應聲揚升，稍早前曾衝上199.6元，飆10.4%；截至上午約9時58分報199元，仍漲10.07%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15595925-%e6%b3%a1%e6%b3%a1%e7%91%aa%e7%89%b9%e6%98%a8%e6%96%a52-51%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bc-%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e4%bb%8a%e6%97%a9%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%9a%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be10",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250724_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 09:59:47",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大族數控昨通過上市聆訊 商米科技傳最快下月IPO集資約1.5億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新股陸續有來，已於深圳上市的大族數控(301200.SZ)昨通過來港上市聆訊；市傳商米科技最快下月招股，集資約1.5億美元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：大族數控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_FI_source-web_301200-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：大族數控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260120_FI_source-web_301200-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：大族數控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大族數控是中國PCB專用生產設備解決方案服務商，主要從事PCB專用生產設備的研發、生產及銷售，現時市值逾580億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據灼識諮詢的資料，按2024年收入計，該公司是中國最大的PCB專用生產設備製造商，中國市場佔有率為10.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"大族數控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/301200-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"大族數控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/301200-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">大族數控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司初步招股書顯示，公司於2022年、2023年及2024年度利潤，分別達4.32億元、1.36億元及3億元；2025年首10個月盈利5.19億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於商米，則是商業物聯網(BIoT)解決方案提供商。根據灼識諮詢的資料，按2024年的收入計，該公司是全球最大的安卓端BIoT解決方案提供商，佔有10%以上的市佔率。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：商米科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250626_FI_source-web_Sunmi-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：商米科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250626_FI_source-web_Sunmi-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：商米科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司擁有逾3年盈利紀錄，於2022年、2023年及2024年度利潤分別為1.6億元、1.01億元及1.81億元；2025年首9個月盈利5607.9萬元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15595886-%e5%a4%a7%e6%97%8f%e6%95%b8%e6%8e%a7%e6%98%a8%e9%80%9a%e9%81%8e%e4%b8%8a%e5%b8%82%e8%81%86%e8%a8%8a-%e5%95%86%e7%b1%b3%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e5%82%b3%e6%9c%80%e5%bf%ab%e4%b8%8b%e6%9c%88ipo%e9%9b%86",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250626_FI_source-web_Sunmi-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 09:53:57",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬指開市升2點 深成指升13點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段微升，上證綜指以4116點開市，升2點或0.06%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報14307點，亦升13點或0.09%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數升2點或0.05%，開報4736點；創業板指數開市報3340點，升2點或0.09%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15595878-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%872%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8713%e9%bb%9e",
